OL,6,FSeveral officers and staff at
OL,7,FLeicestershire and Nottinghamshire
OL,8,FPolice have been issued with gross
OL,9,Fmisconduct notices in responding to a
OL,10,Fsummer camp poisoning case.
OL,12,FEight children and one adult fell ill
OL,13,Fat the camp in Stathern Lodge in
OL,14,FLeicestershire, in July last year.
