OL,3,COfficers served gross misconduct
OL,4,Cnotices after summer camp poisoning
OL,6,F76-year-old Jon Ruben, who was the
OL,7,Fcamp leader, was arrested and later
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to sexual assault of a
OL,9,Fchild under 13, assault of a child
OL,10,Funder 13 by penetration, eight counts
OL,11,Fof child cruelty, three counts of
OL,12,Fmaking indecent images of children and
OL,13,Ffour drug charges.
OL,15,FHe was jailed for 23 years and ten
OL,16,Fmonths.
OL,18,FRuben played a game where he'd go into
OL,19,Fthe boys' rooms and encourage them to
OL,20,Feat the sweets as quickly as possible.
