OL,6,FThey looked like innocent treats, but
OL,7,FRuben went to extreme lengths to trick
OL,8,Fthe children into eating them. A small
OL,9,Ftear on the wrapper shows where he
OL,10,Finjected tranquilliser inside.
OL,12,FTo make sure his wife, Susan, did not
OL,13,Fwake up during his offending against
OL,14,Fthe boys, Ruben drugged her so she
OL,15,Fwould sleep heavily.
OL,17,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,18,FConduct (IOPC) is now investigating
OL,19,Fthe two forces' handling of the case.
