OL,6,FInformation was received by
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police just before 7pm
OL,8,Fon July 27th, raising concerns for the
OL,9,Fsafety of youngsters attending the
OL,10,Fcamp. The detail was logged and passed
OL,11,Fonto Leicestershire Police.
OL,13,FShortly after 4pm the following day,
OL,14,FLeicestershire Police attended the
OL,15,Fsummer camp and arrested 76-year-old
OL,16,FJon Ruben, who later admitted charges
OL,17,Fincluding child cruelty offences.
