OL,6,FTheir enquiries are focusing on what
OL,7,Fhappened in the hours between the
OL,8,Finitial notification and police
OL,9,Fattendance at the camp.
OL,11,FTwo Leicestershire Police officers and
OL,12,Fthree staff members have been told
OL,13,Fthey are under gross misconduct
OL,14,Finvestigation for allegedly failing to
OL,15,Freview the information passed via
OL,16,FNottinghamshire Police, not
OL,17,Fprogressing safeguarding concerns
OL,18,Fpromptly and if this may have delayed
OL,19,Fofficers going to Stathern Lodge.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
