OL,4,Cnotices after summer camp poisoning
OL,6,FTwo police staff members at
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police have also been
OL,8,Fserved with gross misconduct notices
OL,9,Fover the grading of the initial call
OL,10,Fmade to the force, how information
OL,11,Ffrom the call was risk assessed and
OL,12,Fmanaged, and if this caused any delay
OL,13,Fto the police response. All notices
OL,14,Fwill be kept under review as our
OL,15,Finvestigation progresses.
OL,17,FIt follows a conduct referral from
OL,18,FLeicestershire Police on July 29th and
OL,19,Ftheir decision to independently
OL,20,Finvestigate.
