OL,6,FBased on the information provided at
OL,7,Fthe time from Nottinghamshire Police,
OL,8,Fthe IOPC did not consider that a
OL,9,Freferral from the force was necessary.
OL,11,FHowever, following an internal review,
OL,12,Fwhich Nottinghamshire Police shared
OL,13,Fwith them, they advised the force that
OL,14,Fan IOPC referral should be made. This
OL,15,Fwas done in November, and an
OL,16,Finvestigation into Nottinghamshire
OL,17,FPolice began the following month.
