OL,6,FIOPC Director Emily Barry said: "We
OL,7,Fknow that this incident has caused
OL,8,Fshock and distress, particularly to
OL,9,Fthe children and families directly
OL,10,Faffected.
OL,12,F"Our initial enquiries have expanded
OL,13,Fsignificantly, and we are now looking
OL,14,Fat the way both Nottinghamshire Police
OL,15,Fand Leicestershire Police responded to
OL,16,Fthe very serious concerns raised about
OL,17,Fthe children who were staying at
OL,18,FStathern Lodge last summer.
